title: Spain fans rejoice as country clinches first Women’s World Cup title
description: Spain defeated England 1-0 to reach its first Women’s World Cup win as fans watched and celebrated in Madrid and Barcelona.

title: Russian spacecraft crashes into the moon, ending bid to reach lunar south pole
description: Russia’s Luna-25 spacecraft crashed into the moon after it spun into an uncontrolled orbit, the country’s Roscosmos space agency said Sunday.
